{"tid":295532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[HK淪陷20週年]青衣長康邨 女Sales墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-06-23T22:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T22:58:59.000Z","uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35923e9be95926f22f1371f17d3addfdcb83e88a","tid":295532,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T22:58:09.000Z","msg":"青衣長康邨康順樓，凌晨零時許，一名34歲姓黃女子，從大廈高層樓梯墮下，倒臥地上昏迷，保安員發現報警。救護員到場證實已經死亡。警方調查指，死者與母同住，任職Sales，其母指她事發前沒有異樣。警方未有撿獲遺書，調查沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外沙田禾輋邨泰和樓及秀茂坪秀茂坪邨秀景樓，昨晚分別發生兩宗墮樓案件，一男一女死亡。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170624/56869252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170624%2F56869252&d=ZSAgWCCaSfSf8R%2BwuWmvqzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=a9277fbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170624%2F56869252&h=f84d35c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170624/56869252</a>"},{"pid":"0fff789ed7e4dc80e967c6f534317827bbfd109a","tid":295532,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T22:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}